public class SDE
extends BaseWorkspaceLayerSource

Connects an SDE LayerSource with an instance of the ESRI Spatial Database Engine(SDE) product. SDE versions 3.0.2 and higher are supported. Previous definition: An SDE LayerSource connects with an instance of the ESRI Spatial Database Engine product. SDE versions 3.0.2 and higher are supported.
